### 1. Get Audit logs by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Audit logs by Action
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/action/USER_REGISTERED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Audit logs by Action - Goal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/action/GOAL_CREATED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Audit logs by Entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/entity/Goal/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}